snippet.textDisplay:
Guys the real solution is DON'T INTERACT WITH OLD PPL.

No but like unironically, if you have old parents or grandparents nearby help them with supplies so they can stay home, don't come near them when you bring them (at least 2m distance), and if you see an old person out and about in the shop (lots of them don't have anyone to bring them food and stuff so they have to go out), stay your distance from them as well.
